Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:57.79,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(495,478)\fsp5\blur2}火焰的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架势 想动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为骗得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 轰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务可是押送丸铁去京城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人我无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人以及弟弟 都被他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁杀了你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看到这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失火了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火势好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有人在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放火烧你家的歹徒已经查明身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个人称不忍的强盗团伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是冷血无情的极恶之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢完民宅的值钱货之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会杀了全家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了除掉所有的目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母的遗体找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于火势蔓延过快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄的年龄也小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕尸骨无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 忘了你弟弟的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到杀害弟弟和父母的凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却因为任务必须将他押送去京城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是独当一面的警务人员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想因为个人恩怨而影响任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到他早晚会被处死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心总有些冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻眼前的他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在烈焰中杀了弟弟的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是满手血腥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了许多无辜百姓的坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是将他安全地押送到京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管什么任务 他杀了我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许丸铁确实是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个森林是绝佳的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰 你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可在看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 没人会看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 干脆把你也杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在非常冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 只能和你一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 刚才的气势呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别躲了 快现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再欺负丸铁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把丸铁放了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们跟丸铁是什么关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 有话好好说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友舞刀弄枪的很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小孩子下不了手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要替死去的父母和弟弟报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 再仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 丸铁 你别过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些线比钢铁还硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人力是绝对无法扯断的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不忍的文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁我就带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到他 你们就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些线会随着气温上升而缩紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在痛苦中死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半小时后 你们就会四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我可不想死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将丸铁安全押送去京城的任务还没完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 你先搞清自己的状况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都快性命不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得那些不忍会把丸铁当成同伴对待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁没有骗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不忍搞不好会杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想先杀了他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁离开时 不是大喊你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该是有话要告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听那种人渣捏造的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始终觉得丸铁不是十恶不赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在丸铁说出心里话之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈谈吧 一定会有解决方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 可以了 不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以刚才误以为你们是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次任务是负责保护押送丸铁的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能不能放了丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是被丸铁从不忍手中救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子是孤儿 父母都被不忍杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁不忍心杀小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以偷偷背着不忍救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁一直照顾着我们这些孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是不忍干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们的遭遇和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不孤单 我们会陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起 我们就是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要脱离不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再跟他们一起当强盗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做 他们不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定去偷他们的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后故意让警务省逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时 他们为了夺回我 一定会露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样警务省就能将他们一网打尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己当诱饵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后丸铁真的偷了不忍的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们担心丸铁会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来到这座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为不忍会被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丸铁是真心悔过 所以才背叛了不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须想办法抓捕那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正十恶不赦的不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍怎样与我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是救出丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁应该和鸣人在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 丸铁不会被不忍带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去真要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗水渗进去后 绳子就松了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没骗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就习惯这种蛇的毒性了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始终觉得丸铁不是十恶不赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 我要当丸铁的面问个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得找到丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后替父母和我弟弟报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 赶快去救丸铁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要找到他 并亲手杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的确是丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不忍的文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把丸铁放了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿来的小鬼 真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁 他们居然让我把你还给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要还也是还给我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的不忍 我要为家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 给我乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文殊 快放了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说的报仇是怎么回事啊 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.铁丝网
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 这个网坚不可破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我的问题 丸铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就看看我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再伤害他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始乖乖听话不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子是不忍袭击的家庭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷救了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你早就背叛我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 钱就藏在他们那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些钱本来就是这些孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这叛徒 别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了 漩涡鸣人拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 你平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你把丸铁带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸铁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:20:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是不忍的老窝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 明雄应该就在那栋房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放过那些不忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏亲兄弟重逢 简直岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们上吧 浓眉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕敌人曾经是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要一举消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回轰的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各奔前程